   - **\uc0\u916 \u953 \u972 \u961 \u952 \u969 \u963 \u951 :** "\u921 \u948 \u953 \u969 \u964 \u953 \u954 \u942  \u945 \u963 \u966 \u940 \u955 \u953 \u963 \u951 ."\
