5. **\uc0\u902 \u961 \u953 \u963 \u964 \u959  \u960 \u949 \u961 \u953 \u946 \u940 \u955 \u955 \u959 \u957  \u949 \u961 \u947 \u945 \u963 \u943 \u945 \u962 .**\
